 arch/arm/dts/sun50i-a64-pinebook-u-boot.dtsi |  15 ++
 arch/arm/dts/sun50i-a64-pinebook.dts         | 294 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 configs/pinebook_defconfig                   |  22 ++
